main event: A witness observed a strange metallic object over Waikiki Beach, Hawaii, on June 6, 1966.
interesting points: The object was roughly circular in shape,The object traveled in a northerly direction at high speed,It made an abrupt change in direction and accelerated rapidly,The witness obtained several photographs of the object,The report is associated with Project Blue Book.
sighted object: metallic circular object in the sky
witness description: John Doe, who reported the sighting to the National Investigations Committee on Aerial Phenomena
